MODULE TheCSystem implements 'the C system', a causal unicast protocol, described
in

        Michel Raynal, Andre Schiper, and Sam Toueg.
        The causal ordering abstraction and a simple way to implement it.
        Information Processing Letters, 39(6):343â€“350, September 1991.

We also repair a minor bug in the paper: if a process delivers a self-addressed
message, the process eventually becomes unable to deliver messages.

To generate runs:

	% java -jar /usr/share/java/tla-toolbox/tla2tools.jar TheCSystem.tla
